  "status": "Draft",
  "summary": "This proposal introduces a standard for embedding Bonding Curve-like liquidity into Non-Fungible Tokens (NFTs) without modifying the [ERC-721](./eip-721.md) standard. The proposed standard allows the attachment of an embedded liquidity contract, referred to as Tradable Shares, to an ERC-721 NFT. Tradable Shares leverage a Bonding Curve-like approach to attract liquidity, enabling trading of shares based on the bonding curve price formula.",
  "title": "Bonding curve-embedded liquidity for NFTs"
}